query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_rows,
  SUM(CASE WHEN serviceType IN ('l1_euc', 'l1_network', 'smart_hands') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as valid_service_types,
  SUM(CASE WHEN rateUsdCents IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_prices,
  SUM(CASE WHEN isServiceable = 1 OR isServiceable IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as serviceable,
  GROUP_CONCAT(DISTINCT serviceType) as service_types_found
FROM supplierRates 
WHERE supplierId = 12
